{"tid":719553,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實，點解連登仔對牙朗特別苛刻","createTime":"2018-06-27T13:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T14:05:22.000Z","uid":18646,"like":13,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04e7dac9f8895e6fea375d720c16d538e3ae78fb","tid":719553,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:38:33.000Z","msg":"冇入波就話冇入波<br />\n有入波就話唔係致勝球<br />\n<br />\n屌黑面<br />\n屌冇key pass<br />\n屌冇feel<br />\n<br />\n到呢場叫鼓勵隊友一兩句<br />\n又話佢扮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n教練唔選高美斯<br />\n就話牙朗球霸、妒忌<br />\n<br />\n老老實實<br />\n葡萄牙全國上下都旨意你<br />\n想你拎冠軍的時候<br />\n我地呢d外人真係理解唔到佢有幾大壓力<br />\n<br />\n相反阿根廷個邊好似真係冇咩奪冠壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325d1ba3909d9eb47dbdd55f3d7669acc7f3aa8d","tid":719553,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9429408669d179765297bcde5af6688a0683ff7e","tid":719553,"uid":18646,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/719293/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/719293/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n講到好撚慘咁<br />\n牙朗咪又係比人日屌夜屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e97e2105c8d82b99a5ded4cdbced01cc756a0a4","tid":719553,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593274f2118e58db919a65ba0b2e6bcc09dfb2d9","tid":719553,"uid":83933,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,